Package nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.a3.maze.actors

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Actor
    An Actor that can move around on the board and interact with items an tiles.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActorInfo_Impl
    Implements the ActorInfo class and contains the meta data on an actor (e.g Chap or a Bug).
    Bug
    An enemy that moves forwards until it hits a wall then turns around.
    Chap
    The playable character.
    Enemy
    An enemy that can move around the board and harms/kills chap when they come into contact.
